            , was indicted for <rs id="t17900424-72-off383" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17900424-72-off383" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900424-72-off383" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17900424-72-cd384" type="crimeDate">11th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900424-72-off383 t17900424-72-cd384"></join>, a pair of linen sheets, value 5 s. a cotton bed quilt, value 3 s. a pair of linen pillow cases, value 1 s. two window curtains, value 5 s. two iron keys, value 2 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900424-72-victim672" type="victimName">
